  <h2>What is Word Count and Why Does It Matter?</h2>
  <p>Word count is the total number of words in a piece of text. It's essential for writers, students, marketers, and content creators who need to meet specific length requirements or analyse their writing.</p>

  <p>Whether you're writing an essay that must be 2,000 words, a blog post targeted at 1,500 words, or a social media caption limited to 280 characters, accurate word counting is crucial.</p>

