  <ul>
    <li><strong>Twitter/X post</strong> — 280 characters max (not words)</li>
    <li><strong>Facebook post</strong> — No limit, but 63 characters shows fully</li>
    <li><strong>LinkedIn post</strong> — 3,000 character limit</li>
    <li><strong>Instagram caption</strong> — 2,200 character limit</li>
    <li><strong>Blog post (SEO)</strong> — 1,500-3,000 words recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Magazine article</strong> — 800-2,500 words typical</li>
    <li><strong>Academic essay</strong> — Often 2,000-5,000 words</li>
    <li><strong>Short story</strong> — 1,000-7,500 words</li>
    <li><strong>Novel</strong> — 70,000-100,000 words typical</li>
